<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section
      style="
        width: 600px;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
      "
    >
    <div><img src="cid:signUpImage" alt="" style="width: 100%" /></div>
      <article
        class="contContainer"
        style="padding: 14px 40px 34px 40px; margin: 0; box-sizing: border-box"
      >
        <div class="title" style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold">
          회원가입을 축하드립니다.
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: normal;
            line-height: 1.57;
            margin: 20px 0 40px;
          "
        >
          안녕하세요. <span style="color: #c09260"><%= user.user_name %></span>님! <br />
          누리글로벌서비스 회원이 되신것을 환영합니다.
        </div>
        <table
          style="
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
          "
        >
          <tr
            style="
              display: flex;
              border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
              font-size: 14px;
              font-weight: normal;
            "
          >
            <td
              style="
                padding-left: 30px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                width: 110px;
                padding-top: 12px;
                padding-bottom: 12px;
                background-color: #f9f9f9;
              "
            >
              아이디
            </td>
            <td
              style="
                padding-left: 30px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                padding-top: 12px;
                padding-bottom: 12px;
              "
            >
            <%= user.signname %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr
            style="
              display: flex;
              border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
              font-size: 14px;
              font-weight: normal;
            "
          >
            <td
              style="
                padding-left: 30px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                width: 110px;
                padding-top: 12px;
                padding-bottom: 12px;
                background-color: #f9f9f9;
              "
            >
              가입일자
            </td>
            <td
              style="
                padding-left: 30px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                padding-top: 12px;
                padding-bottom: 12px;
              "
            >
            <%= now %>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <div
          style="
            margin: 40px 170px 0 170px;
          "
        >
          <div
            style="
              text-align: center;
              width: 188px;
              padding: 20px 0;
              border-radius: 8px;
              background-color: #c09260;
              cursor: pointer;
            "
          >
            <button
              type="button"
              style="
                font-size: 14px;
                font-weight: normal;
                border: 0;
                background: none;
                cursor: pointer;
              "
            >
            <a href="https://nurl.rsad.work/home" style="text-decoration-line: none; color: #fff;">
              누리글로벌서비스 바로가기
            </a>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article
        class="bottomBar"
        style="padding: 30px 30px 40px; background-color: #f9f9f9"
      >
        <p
          style="
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: normal;
            line-height: 1.83;
            color: #b2b2b2;
          "
        >
          본 메일은 발신 전용으로 답장을 받을 수 없습니다.
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: normal;
            line-height: 1.83;
            color: #b2b2b2;
          "
        >
          ㈜누리글로벌서비스
          <br />
          03189 서울특별시 종로구 청계천로 67, 501호
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: normal;
            line-height: 1.83;
            color: #b2b2b2;
          "
        >
          Copyright© 2022 NURI Global Service Co.,Ltd. All Rights Reserved.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
